text: I tried various types of rice cakes and they were all very delicious. It is great in many ways as a snack for children and as a snack gift for Malay friends. My Malay friends also enjoyed it and said it was delicious. I’ll go often! I ate hard and took only two pictures… hehe
The rice cake is delicious! It looks like you put a lot of effort into making the rice cakes! I’m so glad I got to eat Korean rice cakes abroad! The owner is also friendly, I recommend it! ^^
